# Cross-Customer Observations

> **Scope**: Cross-customer patterns and learnings only. Per-customer state and the active-engagements list are queried live from Notion (filtered by `Customer.Owner`); do not cache customer-specific state here.
>
> Add entries when you observe a pattern that spans ≥2 customers and would help any future session with similar accounts — risks that recur, success moves that generalise, architecture decisions that come up repeatedly, etc.
>
> **Format per entry:**
> - **Pattern:** one-line description of the observation
> - **Source:** customer category and/or session type (no customer names)
> - **Action:** what to do differently or watch for

